OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1780989358
OL,3,CSentence for e-bike teen who killed
OL,4,Cwoman, 86, to be reviewed
OL,6,FLast month, Stokoe, 19, was jailed for
OL,7,Fsix years and nine months by a judge
OL,8,Fat Newcastle Crown Court, having
OL,9,Fadmitted causing death by dangerous
OL,10,Fdriving.
OL,12,FThe Crown Prosecution Service is now
OL,13,Fappealing under the unduly lenient
OL,14,Fscheme against the sentence.
OL,16,FGloria's daughters previously told ITV
OL,17,FTyne Tees they wanted to see the
OL,18,Fsentence reviewed.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1780989358
OL,3,CSentence for e-bike teen who killed
OL,4,Cwoman, 86, to be reviewed
OL,6,FJoanna Donkin, one of her daughters,
OL,7,Fsaid: "We feel because our mam was
OL,8,Felderly does that mean her life
OL,9,Fdoesn't count as much as someone who
OL,10,Fwas younger? Is it because he's
OL,11,Fyounger and he's got his life in front
OL,12,Fof him? Our mam could have lived
OL,13,Fanother 20 years. It's looking like he
OL,14,Fcould have lived another 10 until he
OL,15,Ftook it away from her."
OL,17,FPassing sentence last month, Judge
OL,18,FRobert Adams said he had seen evidence
OL,19,Fof the teenager's regret and sorrow.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
