FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1780989358
OL,3,CSentence for e-bike teen who killed
OL,4,Cwoman, 86, to be reviewed
OL,6,FHelen Towers, defending, said Stokoe
OL,7,Fwas remorseful and had said: "I will
OL,8,Fforever be sorry and I don't expect to
OL,9,Fever be forgiven.
OL,11,F"I wish more than anything that I
OL,12,Fcould change it all."
OL,14,FA psychological assessment found
OL,15,FStokoe had an IQ of 66 and the court
OL,16,Fheard that he has ADHD.
OL,18,FA CPS spokesperson confirmed that an
OL,19,Fappeal has begun under the unduly
OL,20,Flenient scheme.
OL,26,@oD@^OUsD@AOUtD@UO]
