PN,42205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1780989358
OL,3,CSentence for e-bike teen who killed
OL,4,Cwoman, 86, to be reviewed
OL,6,FA spokesperson for the Attorney
OL,7,FGeneral's Office (AGO) said: "We have
OL,8,Freceived multiple requests for Billy
OL,9,FStokoe's sentence to be considered
OL,10,Funder the Unduly Lenient Sentence
OL,11,F(ULS) scheme.
OL,13,F"The Law Officers have 28 days from
OL,14,Fsentencing to carefully consider the
OL,15,Fcase and make a decision."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/5
